    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >许愿石是一款悬疑类文字冒险与探索解谜相结合的游戏，谜题较有挑战性。玩家不仅能够体验精彩丰富的剧情，也能够享受揭开各种谜题的乐趣，并可以探索周围的环境，通过日记、信件、照片、家中物品等来进一步了解故事中的人物，解开艾尔莎身上的重重谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >许愿石一共有7个结局 + 一个特别篇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家讨论Q群: 304589677</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艾尔莎因为机缘从一名魔女那里得到了一块可疑的许愿石。一个小小的愿望引来了意料之外的麻烦，而且事情远比她想象的复杂。艾尔莎逐渐意识到自己的记忆竟然很模糊，似乎忘记了很多重要的事。不合理的事情一件接着一件，身边的一切似乎都渐渐脱轨。待艾尔莎回到家的时候，她发现家已经变样，而家人不知所踪。与此同时，艾尔莎似乎越来越接近某些重要的被她遗忘的东西。有某些深埋的记忆正在逐渐浮出水面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艾尔莎到底是在噩梦中还是现实里？许愿石究竟会引导她走向怎样的命运呢？请帮助引导艾尔莎探索周围的一切，解开重重迷题，做出一次次的选择，找出真相，找回她失落的记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 游戏特色与玩法：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/6a2bb6d940434965b0bdd6a7669c14d4.poster.avif?t=1771046052\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/6a2bb6d940434965b0bdd6a7669c14d4.webm?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/6a2bb6d940434965b0bdd6a7669c14d4.mp4?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>探索周围，从细节和点滴中了解艾尔莎的生活，以及正在发生的一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/a801ecc69dcbd9d35929168503917b34.poster.avif?t=1771046052\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/a801ecc69dcbd9d35929168503917b34.webm?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/a801ecc69dcbd9d35929168503917b34.mp4?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>收集物品，并使用物品与环境互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/1ff35e80e2c5c5c8f0c15b1948ee0df5.poster.avif?t=1771046052\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/1ff35e80e2c5c5c8f0c15b1948ee0df5.webm?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/1ff35e80e2c5c5c8f0c15b1948ee0df5.mp4?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>破解多种多样有趣的谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/4215a579fa129565d4904593f561261f.poster.avif?t=1771046052\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/4215a579fa129565d4904593f561261f.webm?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/4215a579fa129565d4904593f561261f.mp4?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>阅读日记，信件，小笔记等来一步步了解艾尔沙的过去。帮助她破解谜团找回缺失的记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/5c7a5dd173c571fce35297d81d42f720.poster.avif?t=1771046052\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/5c7a5dd173c571fce35297d81d42f720.webm?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/5c7a5dd173c571fce35297d81d42f720.mp4?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>游走在梦境与现实之间，在悠扬动人的音乐中，体验谜团重重，又丰富感人的剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接触剧中的人物，帮助艾尔莎做出一次次的选择。游戏一共有7个结局。</p>",
